PEOPLE
v.
THOMPSON S232212 Supreme Court of California August 16, 2017 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division Four for reconsideration in light of People v. Romanowski (2017) 2 Cal.5th 903, 215 Cal.Rptr.3d 758, 391 P.3d 633.

Corrigan, J., was absent and did not participate.
